                    </placeName> b<supplied>ei</supplied> <placeName type="place" key="Zürich (Stadt)">Zürich</placeName> <lb xml:id="p1-l21"/>  <date when="1858-02-21">21. <choice>
                            <abbr>Febr<hi rend="sup">r</hi> </abbr>
                            <expan>Februar</expan>
                        </choice> 1858</date>.</p>
      </div>
